WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:01.440
You have been deceived once.

2
00:00:01.440 --> 00:00:03.340
You're not going to be lied to again, are you?

3
00:00:03.360 --> 00:00:06.300
Transfer the money first or I won't believe you.

4
00:00:06.920 --> 00:00:08.600
I'm going to ask you one last time.

5
00:00:08.600 --> 00:00:10.540
Will you marry me or not?

6
00:00:10.600 --> 00:00:12.180
If you say no now

7
00:00:12.680 --> 00:00:15.700
He will definitely use tricks to make Xu Yaohua hurt his wife again

8
00:00:20.560 --> 00:00:21.540
I'll go.

9
00:00:23.160 --> 00:00:24.620
All right, Mr. Zhou

10
00:00:24.640 --> 00:00:26.000
I have recorded it.

11
00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:28.360
If you dare to break your promise

12
00:00:28.360 --> 00:00:30.640
I'll make this recording public

13
00:00:30.640 --> 00:00:31.860
Let you fail

14
00:00:32.240 --> 00:00:36.660
Thank you, Miss Xu, for letting me get what I wanted

15
00:00:37.800 --> 00:00:39.100
Let's go, wait a minute

16
00:00:39.480 --> 00:00:40.820
What about the money I want?

17
00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:44.600
I will soon become the wife of Mr. Zhou's famous family

18
00:00:44.600 --> 00:00:46.120
Will your money be missing?

19
00:00:46.120 --> 00:00:47.700
Listen to me say sorry

20
00:00:50.200 --> 00:00:52.860
You better do what you say

21
00:00:56.520 --> 00:00:57.520
You are hurt.

22
00:00:57.520 --> 00:00:58.340
Can't wait

23
00:00:59.360 --> 00:01:02.080
I promised that Xu Yaoguang would never set foot in Harbor City again

24
00:01:02.080 --> 00:01:03.220
I didn't do it.

25
00:01:04.280 --> 00:01:05.080
Excuse me.

26
00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:09.100
Zhou Yanqing, do you really want to yield Rong Yichen?

27
00:01:09.440 --> 00:01:10.700
You don't like me marrying her

28
00:01:10.760 --> 00:01:12.380
I know you did it for pity

29
00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:13.800
But easy to account for

30
00:01:13.800 --> 00:01:15.480
He's not a good person to pity.

31
00:01:15.480 --> 00:01:16.480
You married her?

32
00:01:16.480 --> 00:01:18.720
It doesn't benefit you or the Zhou family in any way.

33
00:01:18.720 --> 00:01:20.460
Mortals cannot marry those who love

34
00:01:21.160 --> 00:01:22.000
Rejection is the same

35
00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:25.140
Is the person he loves me?

